profile_summary: As a skilled web developer with a strong background in JavaScript, TypeScript, and Jupyter Notebook, I've been actively contributing to the developer community through public repositories. With over a decade of experience in software development and a focus on backend development and Angular.js, I'm well-equipped to tackle complex projects. My expertise also extends to integrating frontend frameworks like Bootstrap with backend technologies such as NodeJS, MongoDB, and Express.js.
